0123456789
** ER
E-01 A PRIVATE NOTIFICATION DATA IS NOT INPUT
E-02 A PRIVATE NOTIFICATION DATA IS NOT INPUT DEFINITELY
E-03 ON THIS PRIVATE NOTIFICATION DATE,DATA ARE NOT YET MADE
E-04 RESUITS DATE IS NOT INPUT
E-05 RESUITS DATE IS NOT INPUT DEFINITELY
E-06 ON THERE RESUITS DATE,DATA ARE NOT YET MADE
E-07 A FACTORY CORD IS NOT INPUT
E-08 THE FACTORY CORD PLEASE INPUT A NUMBER
E-09 A RATHER THIN MASTER DOES NOT HAVE A FACTORY CORD
E-10 A PROCESS NAME MASTER DOES NOT HAVE THIS PROCESS CORD
E-11 A PROCESS CORD IN NOT INPUT
E-12 THE OLD AND THE NEW PROCESS JUDGMENT IS NOT INPUT
E-13 THE OLD AND THE NEW PROCESS JUDGMENT IS 1.2
E-14        ON A DATE, IT IS NOT REGISTERED BY A CALENDAR MASTER
